incident_updates.body:
Unexpected delay extended the estimated time of reparation of a fiber cut.
We continue to work with the local operator to fix the issue.
We are continuing to work on a fix for this issue.

Start time : 17/08/2023 07:26 UTC Service impact : Latency is being observed on our backbone between Asia and USA Root cause : 2 fiber cuts caused the incident Ongoing actions : Our teams are currently in contact with our operator to resolve the incident. First fiber cut should be repaired on the 10/09/2023 and the second one on the 30/09/2023.
